  sections:
  - text: 'All routes must have a minimum level of <color=#62B4E8>safety</color>,
      determined by each task. Safety is increased in <color=#62B4E8>low-risk areas</color>:
      sidewalks are the ideal place! Use the <color=#F4C542>left click</color> to
      start building.'
    destroyRequirement: 0
